(firstQuint)Efficacy of Topical Cysteamine in Nephropathic Cyctinosis.

 A total of 26 patients with nephropathic cystinosis were included in this prospective study.

 Patients were evaluated for improvement of corneal cysteine deposits crystals and photophobia following treatment with topical 0.

55% cysteamine eye drops.

